Sentencas: The morphology and particle size of yttria (3 and 8 mol%)-doped zirconia/alumina (0 to 20 wt%) coprecipitated powders were studied using measurements of surface area, X-ray diffraction, DTA, infrared spectroscopy, and TEM.
Titulo: PROCESSING AND PROPERTIES OF ZIRCONIA-BASED/AL2O3 NANOSCALE-COMPOSITES AS ELECTROLYTES FOR SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELLS

Sentencas: Shrinkage behaviour of the isopressed composites was studied by isothermal and non-isothermal experiments.
Titulo: PROCESSING AND PROPERTIES OF ZIRCONIA-BASED/AL2O3 NANOSCALE-COMPOSITES AS ELECTROLYTES FOR SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELLS

Sentencas: The effect of Al2O3 content on the microhardness (H) and fracture toughness (K-IC) of zirconia/Al2O3 composites was studied by the Vicker's indentation technique.
Titulo: PROCESSING AND PROPERTIES OF ZIRCONIA-BASED/AL2O3 NANOSCALE-COMPOSITES AS ELECTROLYTES FOR SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELLS

Sentencas: The influence of Al2O3 addition (10 wt%) on the electrical properties of tetragonal/Al2O3, and cubic zirconia/Al2O3 composites also was studied.
Titulo: PROCESSING AND PROPERTIES OF ZIRCONIA-BASED/AL2O3 NANOSCALE-COMPOSITES AS ELECTROLYTES FOR SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELLS
